title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Canada -  Pinawa Dam Provincial Park
description:
In this video we will fly parallel next to the Pinawa Dam Provincial Park. Pinawa Dam Provincial Park is a provincial park located north of Pinawa, Manitoba, on Hwy 520, overlooking the Pinawa Channel.

It was designated a provincial park by the Government of Manitoba in 1985. The park is 250,000 square metres (62 acres) in size.[2] The park is considered to be a Class V protected area under the IUCN protected area management categories.

The park is home to such fish species as walleye, northern pike, catfish, and smallmouth bass; and such animals as white-tailed deer, black bear, fox, and otter.
